    "content": "Based on your data, it appears that you have indeed reached a weight plateau.\n\nYour weight has been stuck at 73.0kg for the past several days (from March 23 to March 29), with only minor fluctuations. The average daily intake is also relatively consistent, which may not be enough to cause significant changes in body weight.\n\nTo break through this plateau, I would recommend increasing your daily caloric intake by about 250-300 kcal above your current average. This will provide your body with the necessary energy to make progress towards your weight loss goals.\n\nAdditionally, we can also look into optimizing your macronutrient ratios and adjusting your diet to better align with your targets (P146g | C261g | F58g). Would you like me to suggest some tweaks?",
